nodes.text: Zeed Venom was a Guild-sponsored bounty hunter. Venom traveled to Ord Mynock Freeport to collect a bounty. The bounty hunter wore specialized armor.

Depending on which scenario is played, Venom is either trying to collect 25000 credits from Vok or kill him due to an unpaid gambling debt or capture Cambra Del and return her to a loan shark for a reward of 20000 credits.
